Gates Says Iraq Trip May Be His Last as Pentagon Chief, AP Says

-- B y   C a r o l i n e   A l e x a n d e r
-- 
2011-04-07T10:00:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/gates-says-iraq-trip-may-be-his-last-as-pentagon-chief-ap-says.html
U.S. Defense Secretary  Robert Gates 
told troops in  Baghdad  that his unannounced visit to  Iraq  this
week will probably be his last as Pentagon chief, the  Associated
Press  reported. Gates has said he intends to step down sometime
this year, without specifying a date.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Caroline Alexander in London at 
 calexander1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  